Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Briefing-gate to be investigated
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043x8p2
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 10 Jul 1983
Reagan's popularity rating could be hit by criminal investigation into who stole Carter's briefing papers. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less